name: The Hub City - Limited edition Giclee print by Christopher Willingham
description:
Show your love for Hip Hop with a tribute to one of the Cities that has served as a foundation for West Coast Rap - Compton California, the CPT, AKA - The Hub City.  This is a limited edition of 50 - with 45 for sale exclusively through the Art of Cip Shop.

Prints are 12 in. x 16 in. with print surface area of 11 in. x 15 in.

Printed on only the highest quality ph neutral papers using the best pigments - our limited edition giclees are truly museum archival grade.  Each print is inspected, numbered, and signed by the artist to insure only the absolute best prints.

Orders ship within 2-3 business days domestic United States.

name: To the Mothership - Limited edition Giclee print by Christopher Willingham

name: To the Mothership - Original drawing by Christopher Willingham
description:
